=Description=

"On February 9, 2008, Howard Rheingold moderated a panel at the 24-7 DIY Video Summit. Here is Henry Jenkins, Director of the MIT Comparative Media Studies Program, talking briefly about his most hopeful vision for the future of do-it-yourself video, captured from the audience and edited by Ulrike Reinhard."
